<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 13–18" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figures 13 - 18. Distribution of Steninae in Iran. 13. Stenus guttula species group: ○ Stenus erythrocnemus, ● Stenus maculiger; 14. Stenus hopffgarteni species group: ○ Stenus fuscicornis; 15. Stenus humilis species group: ○ Stenus callidus; 16. Stenus impressus and Stenus incanus species groups: ○ Stenus heinzianus, △ Stenus taurus; 17. Stenus latifrons and Stenus melanarius species groups: ▲ Stenus latifrons, ○ Stenus incrassatus, □ Stenus morio, ● Stenus peripherus; 18. Stenus melanopus species group: ○ Stenus atratulus, ● Stenus piscator." figureDoi="10.3897/dez.63.5885.figures13-18" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/74430" pageId="8" pageNumber="25">Fig. 17</figureCitation>
